(Lunaprine, the battles over. Sorry.)

Starscream/Gotron

They both kept a closeful eye on Waspinator and Hell Beast. Gotron 
began to walk away with the group, but before Starscream did, he 
whispered something to Hell Beast.

"If you are a part of this in some way, we'll find you. And than you 
will share the same punishment as Megatron."

He walked off with the group.
